                            <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:normal;background:#FCFBFA;margin:11.25pt 0cm 11.25pt 0cm;"><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-size:9pt;font-family:'source_sans_proregular', serif;color:#333333;">10. GENEL HÜKÜMLER</span></span></p>
